summary: You'll need to eat, drink and rest. Enjoy eating, drinking and sleeping.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]
[b][color=#93c47d]- [u]Check the changelogs for changes[/u] [/color][color=#00ff00](Update completed!) [/color][color=#93c47d]-[/color][/b]

※ [u]The mod will start automatically after one day[/u]. (It starts at 10 o'clock-AM.) : game time.. XD


[b]Your Need[/b]
By default you cannot die from neglecting your needs. Your 'needs' will not exceed 16 hours. (default)
Messages will appear in the upper left corner detailing your current state. (default: every 2hours)
All needs are measured in hours you can go without addressing that need before it begins to affect you.
[b]

[/b][b]The specifics:[/b]
[b]Hunger:[/b] 3 types of food: Minor food, Medium food and Hearty food.
Minor / Medium / Hearty food restore 1/5/9 hours of hunger. [i]

[b]Food ([/b]raw meat, raw food, Sweet food, and cooked food)
 1. Raw meat
Eating raw meat with satiate you but can also harm you.
Raw food has a negative impact on health.

 2. Raw food
Raw food is, uncooked foods, foods in their natural state – nothing more, nothing less. Raw food [color=#93c47d]will gain no effects.[/color]

 3. Sweet food
Sweet food that can feel honey and sugar. If you eat this food, your magicka (or stamina) will be restored. 
Mead, Sweet roll, honey, ..etc.

 4. Cooked food
It is safe from all the debuffs you can get when you eat raw meat. 
[i][color=#93c47d]If you eat stew(or soup), your magicka will be restored.[/color][/i]

[/i]
[b]Thirst:[/b] 3 types of drinks: small, large and special.
Small (alcohol and fruit) / Large (water and milk) / Special (Velvet LeChance (Talen-Jei)) restore 2/5/9 hours of thirst. The stew & soups depends on the main ingredient.
  - Water collected from wells in city. No needs empty water bottle.
  - All alcohol c[i]onsuming alcohol 1 times will put you in a drunken state, produce visual impairment effects.. (it lasts 20 sec) [/i]
  - (Red/Green) Apples and tomatoes are classified as beverages. 
  - You can [color=#93c47d]make juice[/color] using (Red) apples or tomatoes. ([color=#93c47d]non-alcoholic beverages[/color])[i]
[/i]

[b]Sleep:[/b] Any amount of sleep restores sleep to maximum value.[i]
[/i]

[b]Uninstallation:[/b]
Disable the mod through the config spell's disable/enable menu to avoid a bug where the debuff effects will persist permanently after the mod is disabled. This is a problem with the game engine and not with the mod. After disabling in game, deactivate/delete the mod files. I would recommend preforming a clean save to be safe.


[b]Conflicts and support:[/b]
May conflict with other mods that alter food or drinks. This mod does not support unofficial patch. (Only food added as an unofficial patch, [u]not all food[/u])
[s]
[/s]
[b]Credits[/b]
Thank you so much [b][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/21384/]griffinsclaw[/url][/b] and [b][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38507]Thicketford[/url] [/b]and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28091]bfadragon[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/69576]nedellis[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50074]BuGi[/url].
[/size][/font]

files.name: Nord Needs Rebuild
files.changelogHtml:
Update for cannibalism and Werewolf.

Debuff about raw meat when you are Werewolf..
There is a toxicity specific to the raw meat, so even the Werewolf is applied to the debuff.
but, While eating the corpse, the speed of health regeneration is doubled.
and every time eat a corpse, your "needs" are reduced.

If you are "Namira's blessing, Health regenerates 60% faster. (It lasts for 5 minutes) and every time eat a corpse, your "needs" are reduced.

files.name: Nord Needs Rebuild
files.changelogHtml:
Added recipes to make food.
1. Honey
You can combine bees and Honeycomb to make honey.

2. Sweet ale
Magicka is fully restored.

3. Ghost drink
You turn into a form of ghost for 80 seconds.
In the meantime your body is lighter like a feather, your movement go faster.
And move more quietly (for 80 seconds).

4. Required (wooden) bowl
You need a bowl to make soup or stew.

files.changelogHtml:
Falmer Blood Elixir and Philter of the Phantom
* Can be made into cooking pot
* Effect changed.

Falmer Blood Elixir
Heals the caster 1 point
-> Improved night vision for 60 seconds. & Small drink
:: Palmer moves in the dark. / Beer was included in the ingredients.
* The goods that Brynjolf sells also change the effect.
* You can make Falmer drinks in the cooking pot.

Philter of the Phantom
Appear spectral for 30 seconds.
-> Appear spectral for 80 seconds. & Move more quietly for 80 seconds. & Small drink
:: The ghost doesn't make a sound when moving. / Beer was included in the ingredients.
* You can make ghost drinks in the cooking pot.
